8adc215e-5650-4667-b692-3907f9966aa0.00d2c660-28b3-41c4-be30-30e0110a1af8.description=
Adds a list of flow variables to the local context. The variables are available in the current flow and its child flows.

Inputs\:
    keyNames - The names of the flow variables to add, separated by "delimiter".
    myValues - The values to assign to the flow variables, separated by "delimiter".
    delimiter - The delimiter that separates the key names and the values from the "keyNames" and "myValues" input strings.

Results\:
    returnResult - This is the primary output. It contains the value of "myValue" input field.

Responses\:
    success - The operation completed as stated in the description.

Notes\:
1. If the number of variable names is greater than the number of variable values, the value of each variable will be the value of "myValues" input field.
2. If the number of variable names is less than the number of variable values, the additional variable values will be discarded.

step.name: Query Automation DB for Switch ID

staticBinding.value:
Select PSW_SW_ID as switchID, PSW_SW_FROM_PROD as pswFromProd, PSW_SW_TO_PROD as pswToProd, PSW_SW_TERM_EXTN_YN as swTermExtn, PSW_SW_DAY as pswDay, PSW_UPDATE_PDSW as updatePDSW, PSW_UPDATE_FACT as updateFACT, PSW_UPDATE_CS90 as updateCS90, PSW_UPDATE_LBRD as updateLBRD, PSW_UPDATE_CCTP as updateCCTP, PSW_UPDATE_VCHG as updateVCHG, PSW_UPDATE_LNS4 as updateLNS4, PSW_UPDATE_VRMI as updateVRMI, PSW_UPDATE_DATE as updateDATE, PSW_UPDATE_FADS as updateFADS, PSW_UPDATE_TENT as updateTENT, PSW_UPDATE_DRDB as updateDRDB, PSW_UPDATE_VMGD as updateVMGD, PSW_UPDATE_ACHC as updateACHC, PSW_UPDATE_PRCD as updatePRCD
from ${table} where PSW_SW_FROM_PROD = '${fromFilter}' and PSW_SW_TO_PROD = '${toFilter}' and PSW_SW_TERM_EXTN_YN = '${termExtn}' and PSW_SW_DAY = 0
